summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2933, for the improvement of 23rd Avenue West from West Garfield Street to West Lee Street, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle, by repiling the existing bridge structure and replacing sway braces where necessary, under Ordinance No. 35382 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
